Educational games for children which will help your baby spend his time with an electronic device effectively. You will visit Bimi Boo’s friends who live on a wondrous island. You will play developing games with a kittens, funny birds and cute squirrel.

The application includes simple games intended to develop fine motor skills and that will entertain your child with bright colors, nice characters and interesting tasks:

- Arrange object by color, form, number and size;
- Use logic when selecting series of items;
- Put geometrical figures on the silhouette;
- Sort things in the right order;
- Restore pictures from memory.

Designed for children of preschool age and also suitable for boys and girls 2- 5 years old. All the activities were developed with participation of experts in the field of children education and include such educational elements as puzzles, sorting and logical games.

The application contains the following developing and educative games for children:

- Items sorting – you need to put food into the fridge and clothes into the wardrobe;
- Logic tasks in the game with a train – help cute kittens get home and deliver food for them;
- Thinking activities where your kid will arrange items in the baskets;
- Logical thinking tasks where your child will sort things by their features.

Who says math is hard and boring? Level up your math skills with many interesting math levels! MathBrain learning quiz is a unique app with which you will increase the concentration, reaction, and speed of your brain! You can develop memory, attention, and logical thinking. With every-day constant basic mathematics exercises, you will also develop multiplication, division, subtraction, and addition.

This is a collection of amazing equations aimed at developing your mental abilities. Every day, a record is kept of your successes, which you can analyze every day. All indicators are evaluated on a common scale, and you can easily see what specific skills you need to work on. Train your concentration, speed of reaction, memory, flexibility of thinking, and general knowledge. Information on how your skills develop will be available in your profile, and you will easily understand what else you can work on.

Features:
- Reminders for regular exercise;
- Bright and easy-to-use in-app design;
- Ability to purchase multiple subscription plans;
- Track your progress, with numbers and graphs.
- Various types of training, each of which consists of groups of arithmetic problems;
- Develop memory bypassing 3 different fascinating and difficulty levels;
- You will become smarter, develop and improve mathematical skills, train your brain, improve your memory, learn to focus, concentrate and notice small things, test your logic, hone your reflexes, become agile, train your mind and develop speed;
- It requires a minimum of your time, 2-5 minutes per day is enough for training;

Do you want to check how well your brain works? Or is there a desire to move gyrus? Then this fun intellectual game for memory, speed, and mindfulness is for you! Everything you need to train your brains - you will find in this app!

